{"tid":1249474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區諾軒: 撒離與否不用公投, 市民自行決定去留","createTime":"2019-06-21T17:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T03:53:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"74a9f5ca744d85e87740573718ef03222f7069b2","tid":1249474,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/posts/2273132256057133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finmediahk%2Fposts%2F2273132256057133&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=d25dd36b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/posts/2273132256057133</a><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立媒體網<br />\n51分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n救護員陪同警總傷者離開<br />\n公投無法完成 市民自行決定去留<br />\n<br />\n【即時】(00:30) 救護員步出警察總部，一名老婦、一名孕婦及一名女士分別需要借助輪椅離開，另外亦有10多人隨救護員步行離開。區諾軒之後在場表示，看見警方網上貼文，稱由於有人示威，導致救護員無法進入警總，辯稱明明是警方自己拒絕讓救護員進入，與示威者無關。<br />\n<br />\n另外，區諾軒表示由於救護員事件，現場無法進行公投，他呼籲群眾自行決定去留，並堅持不流血、不受傷、不被補的原則。群眾則高呼「香港人，加油」。<br />\n<br />\n(00:10) 立法會議員區諾軒表示因為救護員事件，導致公投延遲。他說會在救護員離開後才舉行公投，但因可能來不及港鐵尾班車，呼籲群眾自己衡量。"},{"pid":"006164c444fc5466f9f7d30dcbf877f1840b25b4","tid":1249474,"uid":228337,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"487f4b60d0eb821dd9b9d3459e527b1135452668","tid":1249474,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:34:20.000Z","msg":"區諾軒係咪鬼上身? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42952a72a5abfd52909a09899e1e21ea00e526b0","tid":1249474,"uid":36134,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"呢d先係路"},{"pid":"2037959d3310f07dd6fc40233798f7448b1e29b8","tid":1249474,"uid":169074,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c032309e0cebe5074acd942eeec03e4fe929f59","tid":1249474,"uid":33875,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score"